!!! PLEASE NOTE: The 'base/admin/' directory is not protected in any
way! You have to protect it yourself with .htaccess or other measures!

THIS IS ALPHA SOFTWARE! It basically works for me, but there is no
guarantee whatsoever that it will work for you at all. You will find
a lot of bugs, please report them using the bugtracker on SourceForge:

http://sourceforge.net/tracker/?func=add&group_id=32699&atid=406296

Before you post a bug, please make sure nobody else already reported
the same bug, by browsing the bug database:

http://sourceforge.net/tracker/?func=browse&group_id=32699&atid=406296

For installation instructions, please see the INSTALL file.

If you need help, please visit the the Help Forum:

http://sourceforge.net/forum/forum.php?forum_id=102858

